snippet.title: Go! Go! Kokopolo - Anniversary Collection (Nintendo 3DS) - Trailer │2022 Limited Run Games
snippet.description:
To celebrate the 10th Anniversary of the Nintendo DSiWare classic "Go! Go! Kokopolo - Harmonious Forest Revenge", Tanukii Studios and Limited Run Games present possibly the final ever Nintendo 3DS physical release - "Go! Go! Kokopolo - Anniversary Collection"!!!

Includes:
- "Go! Go! Kokopolo - Harmonious Forest Revenge" (2011)
- "Go! Go! Kokopolo 3D - Space Recipe For Disaster" (2017)

Extras (Included in Collector's Set):
- "Go! Go! Kokopolo - Original Soundtrack Volume 01" (2022)
- Limited Edition Kokopolo Anniversary Collectors coin
- 4 Exclusive Sticker Sheets

*Pre-order details to be announced soon!*

https://limitedrungames.com/
https://www.kokopolo.com/
https://twitter.com/TanukiiStudios

(compatible with NTSC 3DS systems only)
